    "id": "invalid-passengers-zero",
    "description": "Normalizer corrects passengers=0 to fallback 1, so post-normalization this is valid. Tested as expected behaviour.",
    "expected_ok": true,
    "rationale": "The normalizer's positive_int() silently upgrades 0 to the fallback (1). The validator sees the corrected value and passes.",
